{"type": "article", "id": 22441, "title": "这个设计了不起之“斯德哥尔摩家具和照明展”（下）", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。\r\n", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 6794, "name": "斯德哥尔摩家具展"}, {"id": 23565, "name": "Fogia"}, {"id": 19566, "name": "Note Design Studio"}, {"id": 23566, "name": "Mutina"}, {"id": 16555, "name": "wastberg"}, {"id": 16270, "name": "Industrial Facility"}, {"id": 23567, "name": "fredericia"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}, {"id": 23569, "name": "Thom Fougere"}, {"id": 23570, "name": "Markus Johansson"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134442TpOtjDPM9ACWwrks.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>taro &amp; pon &amp; kile by fredericia &amp; Jasper Morrison</h2>\n<p>丹麦家具品牌  fredericia 和英国设计师Jasper Morrison 合作了这组家具，包括边桌、沙发和餐桌。他们想要去除所有装饰和不必要的细节，家具都保留的基本形态。其中绿色的沙发靠背和扶手从侧面看是垂直的，但内侧是柔和的弧形，沙发扶手从靠背向外逐渐变窄，似乎连成一体，非常优雅大方。而几款圆形边桌有多种型号选择，可以随意组合或单独使用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134425mnzCNlZPgVKsDy15.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134426Hf7s6dZyr8ClzPSv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134427Jr0v5w4W1oUC9aGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344272eD1SQg5P6mIULRW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63325183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344287Q4oGbIqhylgmPaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94987775\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Arch shelving by Note Design Studio &amp; Fogia </h2>\n<p>瑞典设计事务所 Note Design Studio 带来了一组带有半月结构的书架。书架的外形方正简单，在镂空的两侧加上了半月式的弯曲结构，有点像倒立的拱。当光线照射在上面时，会产生弧线的阴影，就像在墙上印出了花纹。它的实现了功能的最大化，还带给书架一份优雅的古典色彩。<a href=\"http://www.fogia.se/en/product/cabinets-storage/arch-2/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134429LhKv0yObZ25rGeYd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85683761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344308GJ1U43HERs7WpNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134430I3Vb69h2yj1EMYzf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134431ShK5as2G60vOtycd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134432TZt0PRapMJnqEXSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Numi &amp; Numini by Konstantin Grcic &amp; Mutina</h2>\n<p>德国设计师 Konstantin Grcic 曾与意大利瓷砖品牌 Mutina 合作了一组瓷砖设计，一共有 6 种花纹。每种瓷砖都有几何式的图案，一部分经过上釉，另一部分是粗糙的，它们之间有了深浅的变化，像是图像上的阴影。Numini 的型号比 Numi 更小，在瓷砖表面以浮雕的手法制作，排列后也有光影的效果。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134432coO7MijmCdeZKHVb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134433ElaYsGxnk760RdUu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344339TpYfLt1QzJ24aEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134434CYwH01hUWaOmMnZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344342o4VpBtcdlf8NAMu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>极简家具组 by Thom Fougere </h2>\n<p>这组家具来自加拿大设计师 Thom Fougere ，除了木质家具外还包括放壁炉工具的小件和石灰岩桌子。他认为北欧、日本和加拿大在地理上有相似之处，这组家具有类似简洁实用的风格并注重保留材料本身的特征。或者用一块大的石灰岩当桌面，或者在木桌上使用编织元素，有一款小的边桌是几何图案的结合，圆桌面搭配三角形结构，另有一些小的圆柱装饰，在实用中带有趣味性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134435C3Y4buAVc6ihSmok.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344358WHgC1mjQqGOLaKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134436RLFkJt9am4S3ZOhK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01495726\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134437KjNlpF7vBaxHyq4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134437Iyb4GgceEPvVJ3LW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134437teyENXYhvTJCLbao.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>“w162 dalston照明灯” by wästberg &amp;industrial facility</h2>\n<p>瑞典灯具品牌 wästberg 在家具展上带来了一款 w162 dalston 照明灯，由 industrial facility 设计。这款灯的外形是仓库或工作室里最常见的一种，但就是这样看似简单的灯非常坚固耐用。灯罩有金属或玻璃两种，可安装 LED 灯，不同色彩组合在一起后有独特的艺术感。<a href=\"http://www.industrialfacility.co.uk/page/projects/lighting/dalston-lamp\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134438eglmEAIKWkzPV0vp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66259169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134438eVOotd4fmpGWzHTr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60268949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134439v9G6IBH4wr5WUnsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134439pKw7xdrmGCVMg6ov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65281174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134440gm0ex7OFTl9jQIuP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>mopey by Markus Johansson </h2>\n<p>这是瑞典设计师 Markus Johansson 带来的一组咖啡桌，在方形桌面旁连接了一块略高的圆形桌面，都是橡木做的。它真正的用途在于不同颜色和型号的咖啡桌可以拼在一起，利用错位的高度让他们形成一个新的拼桌，可以适应不同的需求，也让空间显得有趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134440MSf8ZYDU1jRrtuXA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134441v5lPc6usEeBgJVx1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75672372\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134441NTgcmBA74fUz9MR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134441EnW9wDVrgZuXHb2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134442HwKAIcErRJSst7Bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}